column5: I totally relate to all of this, especially right now with all that I'm doing with my 9-to-5 and my side job and helping friends and family, when most days it's hard enough taking care of my basic needs. It takes a toll. I'm just waiting for the bottom to drop out as always. Most people really don't know the struggle.
Yes, yes! More if this!!!! I wish my friends understood.
Hey friend, just want to say, you matter and you are loved. Want to talk?
